          <span id='video3'/><span id='video'/><span id='video2'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>video</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <div class='bd-edctl'>
              <a class='bd-edctl' href='#' onclick='return show_hide(this, &quot;opt_video_1&quot;)' title='注釈を表示'>[+]</a>
            </div>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>1. ビデオ</p>
            <div id='opt_video_1' style='display: none;'>
              <p class='bd-desc'>用例: video CD/DVD, video card, video driver, video port, video chat, video camera, video conference</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <div class='bd-edctl'>
              <a class='bd-edctl' href='#' onclick='return show_hide(this, &quot;opt_video_2&quot;)' title='注釈を表示'>[+]</a>
            </div>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>2. 映像</p>
            <div id='opt_video_2' style='display: none;'>
              <p class='bd-desc'>音声に対する映像</p>
              <p class='bd-desc'>用例: video input/output, video capture, video device, video track, video channel, video stream, video sampling rate, video bitrate</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <div class='bd-edctl'>
              <a class='bd-edctl' href='#' onclick='return show_hide(this, &quot;opt_video_3&quot;)' title='注釈を表示'>[+]</a>
            </div>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>3. 動画</p>
            <div id='opt_video_3' style='display: none;'>
              <p class='bd-desc'>静止画に対する動画</p>
              <p class='bd-desc'>用例: video file, video file format, video codec, video player</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-odd'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='viewer'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>viewer</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>ビューア</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-even'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='view_mode'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>view mode</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>表示モード</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-odd'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='virus'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>virus</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>ウイルス</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-even'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='volume_down'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>Volume Down</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>音量を下げる</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-odd'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='volume_up'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>Volume Up</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>音量を上げる</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-alsep'>
        <td class='bd-alsep-al' colspan='2'>W</td>
      </tr>
      <tr class='bd-entry-odd'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='wallet'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>wallet</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <div class='bd-edctl'>
              <a class='bd-edctl' href='#' onclick='return show_hide(this, &quot;opt_wallet_1&quot;)' title='注釈を表示'>[+]</a>
            </div>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>ウォレット</p>
            <div id='opt_wallet_1' style='display: none;'>
              <p class='bd-desc'>KWallet がパスワードを格納する入れ物</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-even'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='web_browser'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>web browser</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>ウェブブラウザ</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-odd'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='wep_key'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>WEP key</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>WEP キー</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-even'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='whole_words_only'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>whole words only</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <div class='bd-edctl'>
              <a class='bd-edctl' href='#' onclick='return show_hide(this, &quot;opt_whole_words_only_1&quot;)' title='注釈を表示'>[+]</a>
            </div>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>単語単位</p>
            <div id='opt_whole_words_only_1' style='display: none;'>
              <p class='bd-desc'>検索のオプション。文字列の両端に単語境界がある場合にのみマッチします。"file" は "files" にマッチしません。</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-odd'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='widget'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>widget</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>ウィジェット</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-even'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='wired'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>wired</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>有線</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-odd'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='wireless'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>wireless</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>ワイヤレス</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-even'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='wizard'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>wizard</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <div class='bd-edctl'>
              <a class='bd-edctl' href='#' onclick='return show_hide(this, &quot;opt_wizard_1&quot;)' title='注釈を表示'>[+]</a>
            </div>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>ウィザード</p>
            <div id='opt_wizard_1' style='display: none;'>
              <p class='bd-desc'>複雑な設定やタスクを対話形式で順を追って行うユーティリティ。cf. <a class='cref' href='#assistant'>assistant</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-odd'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='working_copy'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>working copy</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>作業コピー</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr class='bd-entry-even'>
        <td class='bd-oterm'>
          <span id='working_folder'/>
          <p class='bd-otline'>working folder</p>
        </td>
        <td class='bd-tterms'>
          <div class='bd-ttgroup'>
            <p class='bd-ttline'>作業フォルダ</p>
          </div>
        </td>
      </tr>

    </table>

  </body>
</html>
